A Quirrell n-xi´ t-xo´n tib´ toj kya´j ​​extzen n-ok t-xo´n tib´ ti´j Harry, jun tq´ob´ ti´j t-xu´k Harry. N-chi kub´ tz´aq kyi´j t-xaq. A ab´j n-ku tz´aq twitz Harry tej t-xi t-xo´n Quirrell. A Harry n-chi tzaj t-xob´il extzen n-chi ẍch´in. Jun paqx, a Harry n-ok tq´o´n tq´ob´ tib´aj tq´ob´ Quirrell, n-chi jyon tu´n t-xi t-xo´n. N-chi tzaj sib´ tjaq´ tq´ob´.

