tu´n t-xi ky-q´o´n ky-xu´k, n-chi b´et ky-b´et, n-chi b´et ex n-chi el kyi´n
t-xaq tze´ n-chi tzaj ky-q´o´n ky-b´e.
t-xe´l kye, a Bludger n-chi tzaj t-xnaq´tza´n, n-chi tzaj t-xiten
BEAMS tza´n t-xi t-xo´n Harry.
