tjunalx n-chi b´et t-xo´n tib´aj jun tze´. Tu´n t-xob´il, a
n-chi jyon tu´n t-xi t-xo´n. nimxix amb´il. Broom n-ok tmojb´an tib´ tuk´e viga extzen Malfoy
