137 INT. GREAT HALL - NIGHT 137

A xob´il extzen a q´oj n-el kyi´n, aye mes te jay n-chi b´aj ky-b´ajsa´n tuk´e
tzalajb´il ex q´uqb´il kyk´u´j... kykyaqil extzun aye Slytherins,
