50 EXT. QUIDDITCH PITCH - MORNING 50

      A Harry n-chi jyon -- noq ch´in t-xilen -- tun t-xi t-k´amo´n
      t-xim kye xjal n-chi ky-ok te b´inchal Quidditch
      b´aj kychmon kyib´aj twitz tx´otx´.

