                at jun t-ximlal Beater, mya
                n-ximana? A xq´uqil il ti´j tu´n tten
                ágil, jurat --

      A Cormac n-ok t-xo´n a FLY kyxol kab´e tq´ob´, n-ok t-kyim a BUZZ.

