      ninfa de madera, luego vuelta, su RISA burlando de él. S´e´n
      n-chi lpe´, FIRE SNAKES kyxol qe t-xaq t-xaq t-xe´.


      AK´AJ ANGLE

      Fred, George, Ron extzen Arthur n-chi b´et ky-b´et, n-chi b´et ky-b´et,
      ky-qan n-chi ky-xo´n SPARKS tze´nku SHADOWS n-chi b´aj t-xiten
      toj tkyaqil t-xaq tze´. Ik tten jlu ik tzeʼn in che ok lpeʼye kyiʼj anjel.


      AK´AJ ANGULES
      A Ginny, t-xmakal te cobre n-chi qoptz´aj, n-chi b´et kyxol t-xmakal.

      A Bellatrix n-xi t-xo´n Harry, n-tze´n t-xu´k.

      A Ginny n-ok t-xo´n tib´, n-ok t-xo´n t-xu´k extzen n-ok tka´yin
      toj marsh n-chi q´aq´in. JUN CHʼIN FIGURA N-XIʼ CHʼIYBʼIL toj jun
      velo te sib´. A t-witz Ginny n-chi ch´expaj, n-ka´yin Bellatrix n-chi b´et
      twitz kyxol qe t-xaq tze´, exttzen SHIFT t-xe t-xe tze´nku a velo te
      n-el t-xupin sib´, n-ok t-xnaq´tza´n... Greyback. Bellatrix n-b´inchen
      jun tq´ajq´ajel twi´, CLICKING -- tze´nku jun señal -- extzen Greyback
      n-chi b´et twitz, n-chi el t-xo´n qe t-xaq twitz
      extzen n-chi yek´un...

      ... Harry tza´n t-xi t-xo´n twitz.

                                  GINNY
                   Myia, Harry! jun tramp!
      A Harry n-chi tzaj t-xob´il, n-chi tka´yin ti´j tq´ajq´ajel twi´ Ginny extzen n-chi tka´yin
      Greyback. A Bellatrix n-chi kub´ we´ t-xu´k, n-chi b´et toj t-b´e
      extzen, n-chi tka´yin Ginny, n-chi ẍch´in tuk´e t-xob´il. N-chi jaw t-xo´n t-xaq,
      n-chi tzaj t-xo´n jun BOLT te LUZ ROJA n-chi tzaj t-xo´n toj jun DUCHA
      te SPARKS ttxlaj Ginny. A Ginny n-chi tzaj t-xo´n, extzen n-chi tzaj t-xo´n
      najchaq, n-chi tzaj t-spik´umal kyxol t-xaq tze´ extzen n-chi ul twitz twitz
      tukil...

