                             DUMBLEDORE
                Ma qe tzak'j? n-chi jaw lab´ine qa
                mya aya.

                              HARRY
                myia b´i´n wune -- ti
                ma b´aj?

                              DUMBLEDORE
                Atzun jlu bʼalo mas nim toklen
                nab´il ma tz´ok nchmo´ne. Ax ikx
